						               													<description>You are a Preacher and you made a deal with the Devil to live 100 years more, and to fulfill your end of the deal, you must collect a 100-year worth of souls. Souls of sinners. To do that, you lure the sinners into your church to &amp;ldquo;repent&amp;rdquo;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You start with a Murderer in your church, then summon 1 of the 9 Demons to choose from, and start luring the sinners to your church. There are 9 kind of Sinners to lure to your church, 7 Sacraments to perform and 1 Good Samaritan to help out, and each has a special power! Make sure your murderer stays in your church so that you can collect the souls of sinners!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is played over a series of rounds. In each round, players draw fresh hands of cards, take turns playing cards until the round is finished, and then do the scoring. First to collect 100 (or higher) souls, wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Sinners was in 2019 Two-Player PnP Game Design Contest and it was the 2nd Best Gateway Game :)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
